    "description": "<p>THYE HUA KWAN NURSING HOME LIMITED</p>    <p>HEALTHCARE/ LIFE SCIENCES/ BIOMEDICAL/ PHARMACEUTICAL/ MEDICAL SERVICES</p>    <p>Thye Hua Kwan Nursing Home @ Hougang will serve 285 residents, including 114 residents with dementia.  We believe in providing the best quality of life for aging Singaporeans and will strive to facilitate aging in the community. To do that, the Nursing Home will consider all psychosocial, physical, medical and emotional aspects of our clients and create a tranquil, person-centred and safe environment for them.</p>    <p>With our mission \"To serve Mankind\", Thye Hua Kwan endeavors to help anyone who needs help with full respect to their race, creed, language, culture and religion, to assist them in every way possible.</p>  ",
